This will prevent the LED from blinking. This pin is listed as an acceptable GPIO IRQ pin [here]( https://github.com/ARMmbed/mbed-os/blob/master/targets/TARGET_RENESAS/TARGET_RZ_A1H/gpio_irq_api.c#L65). It does not print the warning "pinmap not found for peripheral" that would indicate that the pin is not supported for this operation. 

